1. *Morali* smo se da idemo na posao. (We had to go to work.)
2. Oni su nas *moralili* da ostanemo ćutati. (They made us stay quiet.)
3. Imamo *moral* da pokažemo poštovanje. (We have the duty to show respect.)
4. Njegova reč je *morala* da nas inspiriše. (His word was supposed to inspire us.)
5. Ona je *morala* da bude tu. (She had to be there.)